{"tid":254224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重返28年前集會地 導賞團本土視角細說六四","createTime":"2017-05-23T04:53:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T05:20:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bc788277b761d5d092499b49632a1496007dae6","tid":254224,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:53:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170523/20030343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170523%2F20030343&d=og%2B7FzeuXIWaWzWnPnBF5ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=06571a6d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170523%2F20030343&h=7f095682\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170523/20030343</a><br />\n<br />\n重返28年前集會地<br />\n導賞團本土視角細說六四<br />\n<br />\n3,702<br />\n ■陳景輝（中）等人近年舉辦六四導賞團，第一站來到跑馬地。　何頴賢攝<br />\n適中字型<br />\n較大字型<br />\n■陳景輝（中）等人近年舉辦六四導賞團，第一站來到跑馬地。　何頴賢攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】會有一天，夏慤道化海成沙，彌敦道被時日輾碎，催淚彈、胡椒噴霧走進歷史，老舊黃絲帶被唾棄一如維園的燭光&mdash;&mdash;過氣的時代符號。社運人陳景輝不甘六四的一切埋在柏油路下，透過導賞團與新生代重返當年集會重地，述說28年前的人和事，從本土視角重新繪製那時的熱血記憶，寄望港人正視同屬本土的八九歲月。<br />\n記者：馬志剛<br />\n<br />\n近年本土思潮冒起，六四屠城被視為「鄰近地區內部事務」，切割不關注成校園潮流。陳景輝與文化人江瓊珠反其道而行，合辦六四導賞團，在剛過去的5月21日舉行新一輪導賞，第一站來到跑馬地。1989年同日香港有100萬人大遊行，跑馬地馬場正是遊行終點集會所在地，同日支聯會正式成立；之後的「民主歌聲獻中華」與「黑色大靜坐」亦在此舉行。陳景輝形容那是港人「覺醒」里程碑，香港自此不再只是「馬照跑、舞照跳」的拜金城市。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n■跑馬地馬場是當年100萬人大遊行終點集會所在地，「民主歌聲獻中華」與「黑色大靜坐」亦在此舉行。　資料圖片<br />\n <br />\n新華社員工曾掛支持橫額<br />\n第二站是伊利沙伯體育館旁邊小巷，對面就是當年的新華社。那時候學生在新華社門外發動絕食靜坐抗爭，到中國總理李鵬5月19日宣佈北京學運是動亂，當晚有大批市民自發前往小巷聚集，通宵討論事態，5月30日正式成立為「民主台」。<br />\n舊新華社現址是一家酒店，在1989年的時空是中國大陸駐港最高機構。陳景輝說，當年有員工在門外掛上「堅決支持北京學生愛國民主運動」橫額，社長更仿效趙紫陽慰問門前絕食學生，「你想唔想像到，去中聯辦示威，中聯辦啲人走出嚟話支持你？」他指港人拒絕承認屠夫政權、反共等意識，正在此時形成。<br />\n導賞團再到中環遮打花園。這是當年5月4日本港13間大專院校共3,000多名學生遊行後集會所在地，陳景輝指，那個年代有幾千人遊行集會，對社會而言很大震撼，亦為香港日後以遊行集會作為表達訴求的方式奠定基礎。<br />\n陳景輝指，若今天要立足本土抗爭，不可能繞過當年香港發生過的事，「如果冇八九，相信香港人未必知道廣場佔領係爭取民主嘅方式，未必會對青年學生做先鋒有額外支持，亦唔會有2014年佔領嘅土壤」。陳冀港人回想當年如何從支援北京學生，創立出今日香港的民主條件，「遺忘八九六四，就好似本土忘記本土」。<br />\n<br />\n97年主權移交至今，香港前進還是倒退？「蘋果」與你細數廿載風雨。<br />\n【回歸二十年】專頁：<a href=\"http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhksar20.appledaily.com.hk&d=og%2B7FzeuXIWaWzWnPnBF5ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f2d0a8ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hksar20.appledaily.com.hk</a>"},{"pid":"a8802d5b103482a58d510803047fcdb74ea72819","tid":254224,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:54:01.000Z","msg":"■跑馬地馬場是當年100萬人大遊行終點集會所在地，「民主歌聲獻中華」與「黑色大靜坐」亦在此舉行。　資料圖片<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170523/large/23ls2p02z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F23ls2p02z.jpg&h=a613e8bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1662b4e3e168c90f240f0cce1f55088c557253d","tid":254224,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170523/large/a0901a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170523%2Flarge%2Fa0901a.gif&h=a0dfc5fb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06ef89b774ddcd3732928bef316d18f5f7f4bd6d","tid":254224,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T04:54:56.000Z","msg":"■陳景輝（中）等人近年舉辦六四導賞團，第一站來到跑馬地。　何頴賢攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170523/large/23ls2p01z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F23ls2p01z.jpg&h=9f9ed47e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bcde8a15a5c5d0c0cdb2d40c56a6fee425962d7","tid":254224,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:11:15.000Z","msg":"食屎狗左膠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813fa1f05b09cf785a76fa114a3cbc266404dbf0","tid":254224,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:11:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>■陳景輝（中）等人近年舉辦六四導賞團，第一站來到跑馬地。　何頴賢攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170523/large/23ls2p01z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170523%2Flarge%2F23ls2p01z.jpg&h=9f9ed47e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢個樣, 10年都仍然係ON<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樣"},{"pid":"fe2695421f6c77ada7e05bf32246279e87258e94","tid":254224,"uid":39796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食屎狗左膠。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要扮本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db56610bb3b6be7a399dff4290015e62106c8b3d","tid":254224,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hka8964.files.wordpress.com/2015/09/hongkonghistory_1989-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhka8964.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F09%2Fhongkonghistory_1989-4.jpg&h=f59cd934&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7c145cf962d96afc2c48746f9e8b6d35d934df0","tid":254224,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20140520/large/1400570933_2690.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20140520%2Flarge%2F1400570933_2690.jpg&h=b10e5877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01ea9612ca66cf8f5ebc45b7d9a9b3ecedcbb246","tid":254224,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"2014年05月20日<br />\n<br />\n四萬港人8號風球下聲援<br />\n<br />\n■89年5月20日，香港懸掛８號風球，四萬市民冒着狂風暴雨遊行到新華社抗議。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20140520/large/a2002a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20140520%2Flarge%2Fa2002a.gif&h=40d76d94&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}